{"tid":170750,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友對我無曬性趣","createTime":"2017-03-25T01:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T18:20:07.000Z","uid":28598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fef3900178c43765e5ce61222597da477b51bc99","tid":170750,"uid":28598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:22:15.000Z","msg":"係咪我已經無曬吸引力 ps4仲吸引過我<br />\n明明已經一齊住 但都好少扑<br />\n個日開到口話以後隔日先扑 但到第二日又係上床就即訓<br />\n係咪已經扑到厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f5b72daf30c57b09580723eec541aee5766baf","tid":170750,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:29:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會係好忙或者有事煩緊冇mood扑？<br />\n一係試下著情趣內衣/制服引下佢<br />\n或者早啲起身含醒佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7f56fe6874deef34be5b980a1724fc3f8c650d","tid":170750,"uid":3270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:29:57.000Z","msg":"正常啦 日日24/7見住重想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煩少震自己搵野做下<br />\n<br />\n利申:過來人"},{"pid":"b56c79c11feb1932506bfc66aab075afe28876d7","tid":170750,"uid":75070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:30:57.000Z","msg":"分開下啦"},{"pid":"c0f30554f964e4171d0eb38d4847b9e3f94be19e","tid":170750,"uid":44549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:32:36.000Z","msg":"日日返工攰到死撚有mood咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"425f34e88ee1bfad9cb963005f118a0959f52df4","tid":170750,"uid":66119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:33:42.000Z","msg":"人地變返直就唔好搞人啦"},{"pid":"6ed556f28a461efa99dc002fea083e1e2611a019","tid":170750,"uid":20757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:33:56.000Z","msg":"袁禮林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162c8f297ccb3618faecfaafd325f9f897b39297","tid":170750,"uid":52699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:35:33.000Z","msg":"證明你自己無興趣囉屌"},{"pid":"0c4f72ca0c1eea726aa7a9d92b4c4ca290a2884a","tid":170750,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:36:36.000Z","msg":"日日見仲要隔日屌？<br />\n<br />\n我諗冇乜可能<br />\n<br />\n一星期2次已經係極限"},{"pid":"a9481c07be7dbdde313009e2bf5f1749c098c3cc","tid":170750,"uid":28598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係好忙或者有事煩緊冇mood扑？<br />\n一係試下著情趣內衣/制服引下佢<br />\n或者早啲起身含醒佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n情趣內衣一開始拍拖已經有玩 唔知宜家仲有無性趣<br />\n佢宜家好似只係鐘意黑絲<br />\n<br />\n我成日都含醒佢啦 無比佢一巴車埋黎都偷笑"},{"pid":"51413648ecdfa411a5638b6b65d84e883a8e47bb","tid":170750,"uid":52699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:40:20.000Z","msg":"係我覺得淨係會覺得你好撚無聊，成個世界得你男朋友一個，無錯初初依種感覺係幾好，但有異性無人性都會慢慢拎返個平衡<br />\n<br />\n你都要搵下啲朋友，搵下新興趣，返下工啦"},{"pid":"4af88147a49a66cc67057cd20081d26835fb318b","tid":170750,"uid":55416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:41:47.000Z","msg":"你個名係袁禮林<br />\n但個樣同副偈唔係袁澧林<br />\n難怪條仔冇性趣<br />\n<br />\n認真,平日放工都已經攰到仆街<br />\n除非條仔性慾好強<br />\n否則都唔會特別想要<br />\n多啲做主動引鳩佢啦<br />\n太易得到手唔矜貴㗎"},{"pid":"6908d043a62c25a9b9bc7c9b3e06452a7dba15d9","tid":170750,"uid":94935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:42:05.000Z","msg":"Cosplay ps4"},{"pid":"aaed4112f045318b281502f04bc33b2667e867a0","tid":170750,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:42:17.000Z","msg":"日日對都厭喇撚頭<br />\n比啲大家空間<br />\n咁樣反而仲好"},{"pid":"5f62b2fcf2d7d40119df572cb1c614a2ecdcc27b","tid":170750,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:42:35.000Z","msg":"不如講下你3圍先啦"},{"pid":"85499b54fe8b701ba8e01a1cdba70095437507aa","tid":170750,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"返工太疲倦，想瞓多d"},{"pid":"c2fab0a24154b127d46e55f90b06b91018b984f8","tid":170750,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:43:11.000Z","msg":"懷疑你係大肥婆"},{"pid":"1523813c237460f7ec861b42fbc6eb3498d5a533","tid":170750,"uid":28598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:44:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個名係袁禮林<br />\n但個樣同副偈唔係袁澧林<br />\n難怪條仔冇性趣<br />\n<br />\n認真,平日放工都已經攰到仆街<br />\n除非條仔性慾好強<br />\n否則都唔會特別想要<br />\n多啲做主動引鳩佢啦<br />\n太易得到手唔矜貴㗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n次次都係我引佢先扑 都未試過佢主動<br />\n決定唔理佢 唔扑就唔扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6f8e23734b6b38247e52d3f68d0888298a9b20","tid":170750,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個名係袁禮林<br />\n但個樣同副偈唔係袁澧林<br />\n難怪條仔冇性趣<br />\n<br />\n認真,平日放工都已經攰到仆街<br />\n除非條仔性慾好強<br />\n否則都唔會特別想要<br />\n多啲做主動引鳩佢啦<br />\n太易得到手唔矜貴㗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n次次都係我引佢先扑 都未試過佢主動<br />\n決定唔理佢 唔扑就唔扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日扑會死"},{"pid":"152b3a010fa820758e464e7a9e369c661a716d1c","tid":170750,"uid":55416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個名係袁禮林<br />\n但個樣同副偈唔係袁澧林<br />\n難怪條仔冇性趣<br />\n<br />\n認真,平日放工都已經攰到仆街<br />\n除非條仔性慾好強<br />\n否則都唔會特別想要<br />\n多啲做主動引鳩佢啦<br />\n太易得到手唔矜貴㗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n次次都係我引佢先扑 都未試過佢主動<br />\n決定唔理佢 唔扑就唔扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁咪就係唔矜貴囉<br />\n試下禁佢慾兩三個月睇下佢主唔主動<br />\n佢想要就話唔方便 餓撚死佢<br />\n<br />\n不過你應該都係性慾強嗰類<br />\n要實行應該有啲難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6600fb2c297fd753ef105c3b6ea14cbf